# Lynx Forge

Lynx Forge is a Java Swing based compiler and development environment project.

## Features

- Custom menu system
- Desktop GUI
- Project management (planned)
- Compiler system (in development)

## Technologies

- Java
- Swing
- IntelliJ IDEA

## Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Void-Turka/java-swing-compiler-template.git
